下面是 main 函数：

```c ins={37-38, 51-56}
int __fastcall main(int argc, const char **argv, const char **envp)
{
  unsigned int seed; // eax
  int v4; // eax
  int n5; // [rsp+Ch] [rbp-14h] BYREF
  unsigned int v7; // [rsp+10h] [rbp-10h]
  int char; // [rsp+14h] [rbp-Ch]
  unsigned __int64 v9; // [rsp+18h] [rbp-8h]

